T1  - What Works in Securities Laws?
AU  - LA PORTA, RAFAEL
AU  - LOPEZ-DE-SILANES, FLORENCIO
AU  - SHLEIFER, ANDREI
Y1  - 2006/02/01
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/02/01
